COPILOT CHEAT SHEET — STRUCTURED FINANCE / CREDIT / MODELLING

HOW TO USE
	1.	Start every new chat with the Global Baseline
	2.	Add one Task Overlay only (A–F)
	3.	Paste Project Context
	4.	Ask the task

Never stack overlays.

⸻

